## Quality Gates and Checkpoints

### Pre-Handover Validation
- [ ] All priority tasks clearly documented
- [ ] File references verified and accessible
- [ ] Contact information current and available
- [ ] Risk assessment completed and documented

### Handover Confirmation
**Next Agent Acknowledgment:**
- [ ] Instructions understood and questions clarified
- [ ] Required files located and reviewed
- [ ] Environment setup completed
- [ ] Work plan developed and approved

### Progress Monitoring
**Check-in Schedule:**
- [ ] Day 1: Initial progress and blocking issues
- [ ] Mid-phase: Progress update and adjustment needs
- [ ] Phase end: Completion validation and handover preparation

## Handover Completion Checklist

### Current Agent Responsibilities
- [ ] All deliverables documented and accessible
- [ ] Knowledge transfer completed effectively
- [ ] Questions from next agent answered
- [ ] Session state updated appropriately
- [ ] Handover protocol signed off

### Next Agent Responsibilities
- [ ] Handover protocol reviewed and understood
- [ ] Required files accessed and reviewed
- [ ] Questions asked and answered
- [ ] Work plan developed and communicated
- [ ] Handover protocol acknowledgment provided

### Session Coordinator Responsibilities (if applicable)
- [ ] Handover process monitored and facilitated
- [ ] Both agents supported during transition
- [ ] Quality standards maintained across transition
- [ ] Overall project timeline protected

